42:13.996 --> 42:14.577
Come be pray.

42:20.845 --> 42:24.530
Lord God, we thank you that you have not left us defenseless,

42:25.346 --> 42:31.033
You have given us every weapon in our armory that we need to defeat this world.

42:32.215 --> 42:53.842
This world that we live in that so deceived, that so against Christ in so many ways, that we have to live in every day, that we're bombarded with stuff that, Lord, you have given us all that we need to overcome the world and to live a strong, true believers in Christ that will stand up

42:54.722 --> 42:57.768
and stand for faith and trust in Jesus.

42:57.788 --> 42:58.790
So we give you thanks.

42:59.671 --> 43:10.712
So Lord, give us the courage and the grace every day to go forth in your name and to trust in you and to be strong in the Lord and the power of his might.

43:10.732 --> 43:15.582
And we'll be careful to give you the honor and the glory in Christ's name.

43:15.602 --> 43:15.762
Amen.

